{"type": "article", "id": 13501, "title": "Nike Air Max 95 致敬背包", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-14T07:46:06Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000300bc1J876EoVqYFuyH.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t2015 年是 Nike 经典鞋款 Nike Air Max 95 的 20 周岁生日，最近 Nike 推出了一款 Nike Air Max 95 背包，致敬并纪念这个经典鞋款。从球鞋转化为背包，他们保留了前者最精髓的特征，比如经典的波浪形鞋面，整齐的尼龙鞋带，荧光绿色等。配色上他们采用的是早在 1995 年初次面市的 “Neon” 配色，对喜欢 Nike Air Max 95 的人来讲是一款非常惊喜的设计。产品售价 110 欧元，<a href=\"http://www.littlewoodsireland.ie/nike-air-max-95-pursuit-back-pack/1460017673.prd\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以购买。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141253KpQuefsRmkw316S8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141254JMTCF3yAVG50gD68.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}